						               													<description>The era of zombies has begun, and they need you to fight all the opponents and manage to be the winner, assemble 4 teams and the best man wins, you will have hours of fun, entertainment and strategy. What are you waiting to take it?.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Zombienation 2060 is a strategic board game that takes place in a world destroyed by a rare zombie virus. Your objective is to take your clan to conquer the world and the last remaining humans.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You take control over one of the four faction of zombies. During your turn, you move your zombies through the map to explore territories to find items or human survivors to add to your army. If you enter a territory already occupied by zombies from a different faction, you have to fight those to gain control over the territory.&amp;#10;The game is played over several rounds until one of the faction kills the leader of one another faction or kills at least 6 special zombies. With 3-4 players, the game can also end by reaching the explosion level of the round track, where the faction with the most territories under control wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's also possible to improve your gaming experience with a free app that provides some level of augmented reality and different missions for every player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
